Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「君が許さなかった世界はこんなにも綺麗だ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「悲しみを生むこと、全てが悪だとでも言うのか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.69,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現実の銃口　突きつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矜持たちが　壊れても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僕は僕でしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:45.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Against the gunpoint, ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'll rise like the break dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I save them for the final day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:54.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dream of the world for me and "fantasia"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's time to go...Unshaken mind!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揺れる視界を薙ぎ払い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愛すべき"正義"を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:18.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}語られない明日のために生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儚さと　痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}狂気だけが走らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全てが還る日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:31.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I face out, hold out to world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「你所不原谅的世界是这样美丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「制造悲伤的一切都是邪恶吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现实的枪口已指向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使矜持悉数破碎崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也仍然只是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:45.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迎着枪口 随时准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会像破晓的黎明那样喷薄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为末日将他们拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:54.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向往着为我与幻想而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是时候启程了…怀着坚定的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去改变世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}清空动摇的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寻找值得热爱的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:18.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为无从诉说的明天而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在虚幻与痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有疯狂在穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一切回归之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:31.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我将勇敢地面对世界
